Description: This package provides the material for the scIGD workflow demo at BioC2024. 
    The workflow comprises two software (scIGD - Snakemake; SingleCellAlleleExperiment - R/Bioconductor) and one data (scaeData - R/ExperimentHub) packages.
    I showcase all three tools, emphasizing the utilization of SingleCellAlleleExperiment and its functionalities on one of the 
    example datasets available in scaeData, for exploratory and downstream analysis across the data layers offered by the data structure.
